Abstract: Tool to monitorice and classify into +700 categories based on Description, tags and Images from Youtube.
          The main components of this tool are Python, Youtube API and Google Cloud Services like Cloud Vision API and Cloud Natural Language based on NLP Algorithms.
          Google Cloud Vision uses API REST y RPC to be trained.
          
WorkFlow: 1. Launches Youtube API
          2. Gets authenticated into Google Services.
          3. Searches by demand in Youtube.
          4. Extracts tags and video descriptions.
          5. Analyzes the words through NLP.
          6. Returns Category and confidence percentage.

Libraries: google.colab, google.cloud.vision, googleapiclient.discovery, google.cloud.language_v1, PIL, MatplotLib, PyAutoGUI, pydrive.drive, oauth2client.client
